item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】M4A - Taylor Swift - Speak Now (Taylor's Version) (Deluxe)
item.description:
Speak Now (Taylor's Version) (Deluxe)
This is the fan made deluxe of Speak Now (Taylor's Version) This version includes a bunch of international, and acoustic remixes. The Live versions of Last Kiss and Dear John from the Eras Tour are included, along with a bonus track Last Kiss (Piano Version) (Taylor's Version). This includes an alternate album cover.
